node.text:
I'm just as passionate off the court as I am on it, and I run multiple businesses creating designs that make women feel confident. The last thing I need during a full day of important meetings is a migraine attack. That’s why I keep @UBRELVY (ubrogepant) with me so I can get quick migraine relief when I need it without worrying if it’s too late to take it or where I am.


UBRELVY is a prescription medicine used to treat migraine attacks in adults. It is not for migraine prevention. In clinical studies, people took UBRELVY up to 4 hours after an attack had begun. Most people had quick pain relief and some even had pain freedom within 2 hours. Do not take with strong CYP3A4 inhibitors. The most common side effects were nausea and tiredness. For full Patient Information see @ubrelvypi For US consumers only
